name: Radio The Shadow
question: help
response: Here are some things to try. You can say Pick up, and then the name of an item to pick it up. You can say Drop, and the name of an item to drop it. You can check what you are carrying by asking, What am I carrying? You can get a detailed description of any room you are in by saying, look around. You can get a list of exits by saying, what are the exits? You can get a list of spells you have learned by saying, what spells do I know? You move by saying, go, and then the direction you want to go. If there is a door to the north, you can say, go north. Or go through the north door. You can simply say, go door, as long as there is only one door. You can go up and down, if it's a ladder or stairs. You can examine things in detail by saying, look, and the name of the item. Clues are often exposed by looking at things. You can look at items, people, monsters, and exits. You can open items that are containers for other items. You can search rooms or items by saying, search room, or search and the name of the item, in case you think there might be something hidden. You can name yourself at any time by saying, my name is, and then what you want to be called. When you meet other people or monsters in the game, you can tell them to speak, or say hello to them. Some items can be read, you just say, read, and then the name of the item. If you have a spell to cast, you can say, cast, then the name of the spell. Or speak these words: say, and the name of the thing you want to say. If you are answering someone's question, just say, say, and the thing you want to say. If you get into a fight, just say, use, and the name of the item you want to use on your turn. Or cast a spell. You can say, run away, if you want to try to escape. You can say, give me a minute, or hold on a second, if you need some time to think. If you have upgraded your account you can say, I need a hint.If you're tired of hearing me say, what do you want to do now after every room description, just say, turn prompts off.You can say, quit game, or game over, if you are done playing. For a complete list, visit our web site at daysfly.com. What do you want to do now?

name: Radio The Shadow
question: stop
response: Thanks your progress has been saved . Create an account at DaysFly.com and say, Alexa, tell Shadow Realm to link my account, or within the game just say, days fly, for additional game features, including hints and saved games. Thank you for playing.
